<h2><b>2. 3Commas</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">3Commas is one of the most recognized crypto trading bot platforms for users who want more control over automated trading. It supports multiple exchanges, customizable bots, TradingView signals, and advanced strategy automation.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Unlike simpler platforms, 3Commas is better suited for users who already understand trading basics. It gives traders more control over bot behavior, entry rules, exit rules, and risk settings. This makes it more suitable for users who want greater control over automated trading logic instead of relying only on preset plans. </span></p>
