<h2><b>3. Cryptohopper</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cryptohopper is a crypto trading bot platform that combines automated trading, strategy design, AI-assisted tools, and copy trading. It is built for users who want more than basic automation and are willing to spend time improving their bot setup.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">One of Cryptohopper’s strengths is its ability to support different strategy styles. Users can create their own trading logic, use marketplace strategies, follow signalers, or apply AI-assisted strategy selection. This gives the platform flexibility for both intermediate users and more advanced traders.</span></p>
