<h3><b>How to Invest</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To invest with Cryptohopper, users create an account, connect a supported exchange, select or build a strategy, configure bot settings, test the setup, and activate live trading. Beginners can start with templates or marketplace strategies, while advanced users can customize more deeply.</span></p>
<h2><b>4. Bitsgap</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bitsgap is an all-in-one crypto trading platform known for grid bots, DCA bots, trading terminal features, and exchange management. It is designed for users who want automated trading tools while still keeping control over their strategy settings.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bitsgap is especially useful for grid trading. Grid bots are popular in crypto because they can place multiple buy and sell orders across a selected price range. This can help traders take advantage of market volatility without manually entering every order.</span></p>
