<h2><b>5. Coinrule</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Coinrule is a no-code crypto trading automation platform. Its biggest strength is simplicity. Users can create automated trading rules using an “if this, then that” structure without writing code.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This makes Coinrule a good choice for beginners who want to automate strategies but do not want to deal with programming, scripts, or complicated technical systems. For example, users can create rules based on price movement, market signals, portfolio changes, or other conditions.</span></p>
