<h2><b>7. TradeSanta</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">TradeSanta is a cloud-based crypto trading bot platform designed for users who want simple automated trading. It supports long and short strategies, grid-style trading, DCA-style automation, and mobile monitoring.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The platform is useful for users who want a straightforward bot system without too much technical complexity. Traders can set up bots, define strategy conditions, and let TradeSanta monitor the market around the clock.</span></p>
