<h3><b>How to Invest</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To invest with TradeSanta, users connect a supported exchange, choose a bot strategy, select a trading pair, set order size and risk parameters, and activate the bot. After launch, users can monitor and adjust the bot from the dashboard or mobile app.</span></p>
<h2><b>8. Altrady</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Altrady is an advanced crypto trading platform for users who want smarter trade execution, multi-exchange management, and bot automation. It includes trading terminals, smart orders, grid bots, signal bots, and risk management tools.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Altrady is more suitable for intermediate and advanced traders. It is not just a passive bot platform. It is built for people who actively manage trades and want better execution tools across multiple exchanges.</span></p>
