<h2><b>9. Gainium</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Gainium is a crypto trading bot platform focused on strategy creation, automation, backtesting, and performance analysis. It is suitable for users who want to build more serious automated trading systems without writing code.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The platform allows users to create bots, test strategies, apply indicators, manage risk, and monitor results. This makes Gainium a good option for users who want to understand how their strategy works instead of simply turning on a bot and hoping for the best.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Gainium is not the most passive choice, but it is useful for strategy builders who want more control and analysis.</span></p>
