<h3><b>Which AI Trading Bots Are Designed for Advanced Traders? </b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">HaasOnline, Gunbot, and Hummingbot are stronger choices for advanced traders who want scripting, self-hosting, open-source control, or professional-level customization.</span></p>
<h3><b>Can AI trading bots make guaranteed profits?</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">No trading bot can guarantee profits. A bot can improve execution, reduce emotional decisions, and follow strategies consistently, but results still depend on market conditions, strategy quality, fees, and risk management.</span></p>
<h3><b>Should I monitor an AI trading bot after activating it?</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Yes. Automation reduces manual work, but users should still monitor performance, strategy behavior, account activity, and market changes. A trading bot should be managed as a tool, not ignored completely.</span></p>
